gobblin.runtime.listeners

Class AbstractJobListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.runtime.listeners.AbstractJobListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JobListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractCloseableJobListener, EmailNotificationJobListener, JobExecutionEventSubmitterListener, RunOnceJobListener

    public abstract class AbstractJobListener
extends Object
implements JobListener
    An abstract implementation of JobListener which ensures that subclasses do not have to implement all lifecycle events.
